<% content_for :title, "Cookies" %>

<div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 md:p-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Cookies</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Our website uses cookies to help the site work properly (for example, keeping track of items in your basket during checkout)
        and to improve your experience.
      </p>

      <p>
        You can refuse non-essential cookies at any time using the cookie banner on the site.
        Please note that blocking strictly necessary cookies may prevent core features (like the basket and checkout) from working.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 pt-2">Cookie categories</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Strictly necessary</span>: required for essential site functionality.</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Analytics</span>: helps us understand site usage to improve performance.</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Marketing</span>: used to personalise offers and advertising.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        If you want to update your preferences, open the cookie banner and choose “Manage cookies”.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
